WRITING.TITLE: Fredbear's Guilt
WRITING.TEXT: You know that pizza place, Freddy's I think. Well before it was Freddy's, it was smaller and it was called Fredbear's. I remember because I used to work there and I was laid off after a while. But I'm writing this as a warning to kids when getting their first job. Anyway, when I worked there, I pretty much had 2 bosses. One named Henry, the other was named... William. My job was pretty simple, I had to wear an animatronic suit whilst bringing pizza to children. My other job was to make sure those little kids didn't get hurt whilst they played. One day in 83' I was with William. It was my first day and it was only February. We listened to a tape, that Peter (phone guy) left for me in case William didn't show up. He showed me how to put the springlock suits but then... HE threatened me at gunpoint. He forced me into the suit and set those locks off. I survived, but that was only one bad experience. The other time.. it was horrible, and it was the most gruesome thing I have ever seen. It was around November, and it was warm outside, there were kids everywhere, because 1983 was a different time where strangers were common but it was a lot less dangerous. Anyway, William brought his kids there that day and I believe it was his kid's birthday. He told me about his family when he forced me into that suit. I don't remember their names, but there was an older brother, a younger brother who was youngest, and then there was the little girl, who looked just like William. I swear, they looked very similar. So it was his youngest kid's birthday, and that kid.. He cried all the time, and he had this.. Toy. Now, this toy was PARANORMAL and I know it. I'll never get over that... thing. It was a Fredbear plushie but those eyes were full of insanity. Anyway, his big brother bullied him all the time, and even took him on stage, which sounds nice, until you consider the fact the youngest was terrified of the animatronics. At his birthday party he got even closer. The brother and his friends all had masks that matched the characters from the TV show, Fredbear and Friends. Freddy, Bonnie, Chica, and Foxy, those are the guys that have their own restaurant today. So the brother teased the youngest, and he and his friends shoved the youngest into Fredbear's mouth. I yelled at them to stop, but I was too late. Fredbear chomped onto the kid's mouth, and I saw his brains coming out. It was so bloody and gory that I ran to the bathroom. His brain tissue was spilling out all over the floor... Blood gushing onto the giant yellow bear, as the bunny sat there. and watched. William was crying, and beating his older son whilst yelling at his daughter for not doing anything. After everybody left, which was 4 hours before the actual closing time, I had to clean it up. At least they took the body. But inside of Fredbear's mouth was a note, it read: "I'm sorry Dad." The next day I read on the news that a child ran away from his home at 11 pm the night before. His name was Michael Afton.
